OL,5,G0500 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FJo and her son Louis host at
OL,7,     FCastley Camp in Otley, Yorkshire.
OL,8,     FKen and Sharon are horrified by
OL,9,     Fstains on their bedding and the
OL,10,     Fdust in the room, and Jo is left
OL,11,     Ffuming over the feedback.
OL,12,G0525 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe last visit is to the Lion &
OL,14,     FSwan in Congleton, where owner
OL,15,     FPaul and manager Matt go all out
OL,16,     Fto win. But Lisa and Keith are
OL,17,     Fshocked by their waterbed and
OL,18,     Fdirty bathroom.
